---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="QANT Strategic Investments L.L.C-FZ" description="Quantitative Solutions & Strategic Intelligence" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Strategic Intelligence. Quantitative Excellence.</h1>
			<p>
				<strong>QANT Strategic Investments L.L.C-FZ</strong> is a premier quantitative consultancy based in Dubai, 
				specializing in high-performance software systems and strategic process optimization.
			</p>

			<section>
				<h2>1. Custom Software Development</h2>
				<p>
					<strong>Rapid Deployment. Zero Compromise.</strong><br />
					We specialize in executing large-scale software projects within accelerated timeframes. Our experienced 
					engineering team delivers robust, scalable solutions tailored to complex institutional requirements. 
					From architecture to deployment, we ensure your mission-critical systems are handled with precision.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>2. Business Process Optimization</h2>
				<p>
					<strong>Precision Strategy for Global Operations.</strong><br />
					We redefine operational efficiency. By auditing and restructuring core business processes, we eliminate 
					bottlenecks and maximize output. Our consultancy services provide the strategic framework necessary for 
					companies to scale rapidly while maintaining lean and agile structures.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>3. AI-Driven Analytics & Process Enhancement</h2>
				<p>
					<strong>Harnessing Predictive Intelligence.</strong><br />
					Leveraging state-of-the-art Artificial Intelligence and Data Analytics, we transform raw data into a 
					decisive competitive advantage. We implement advanced AI modules to automate decision-making and 
					optimize internal workflows, ensuring your business operates at the peak of modern technological capabilities.
				</p>
			</section>

			<hr />

			<section style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #555;">
				<h3>Corporate Information</h3>
				<p>
					<strong>QANT Strategic Investments L.L.C-FZ</strong><br />
					License Number: 2644133<br />
					Address: Meydan Grandstand, 6th floor, Meydan Road, Nad Al Sheba, Dubai, U.A.E.
				</p>
				<p>
					Contact: <a href="mailto:jan@qantstrategic.com">jan@qantstrategic.com</a>
				</p>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
